race.comment: ELITE DELUXE (6) is a smart dog yet to miss the frame, last start scoring at this track (22.32), making it five straight wins. Well placed here and will go close with a clear run. LET ME COOK (7) has been in the placings at her last two runs, most recently when third (22.73) in a Grade 4/5 over 400m at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. GNARLY NALA (1) is better than last start when fourth (22.96) from Box 5 at this track over 400m. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with three wins from four starts. One of the better hopes. PRONTO ROCCO (4) will have admirers again after placing at this track and distance last time out.
